{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionArtificial Intelligence (AI) technology has been used in various fields in our current society [1][2][3][4][5].",
    "AI technology makes an innovative society possible and changes our lifestyles.",
    "For example, automatic car driving [6][7][8][9], face recognition systems [10][11][12][13], and computer aid detection in the medical area [14][15][16][17].",
    "However, AI models are generally based on large data and huge parameters, called big AI models, especially in the computer version (diffusion model [18]) and the field of natural language processing.",
    "The robust Large Language Model (LLM): Generative Pre-trained Transformer (GPT) models [19] make our daily work more convenient and will even change our work life in the future."
  ]
}